description: Breathtaking one bedroom plus den with unobstructed water views and private balcony at 50 Liberty, the Seaport's premier residences! This rarely available and meticulously designed home boasts sweeping views of Boston Harbor and a spacious open-concept floor plan ideal for entertaining and watching the sun rise. The designer kitchen features sleek white cabinetry, large breakfast bar, and Wolf/SubZero & Miel appliances. En-suite primary bedroom offers ample closets and an oversized double vanity & beautiful marble shower. The additional den comfortably fits a bed and has its own full bathroom making it perfect for guests or a home office. Additional unit features include floor-to-ceiling windows, soaring 10 foot ceilings, hardwood floors throughout, custom closets, Lutron shades, sun-splashed private balcony, in-unit washer/dryer, and one deeded garage parking space. Amenities include 24-Hour concierge and doorman, magnificent clubroom with terrace, fitness center,and conference room.
